{"word":"κριτής","slug":"κριτής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰριτής, οῦ, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κρίνω\">κρίνω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> judge,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on official legal role <b><a href='B:470 5:25'>Mt 5:25</a>; <a href='B:490 12:14'>Lk 12:14</a>, <a href='B:490 12:58'>58</a>; <a href='B:490 18:2'>18:2</a>; <a href='B:510 10:42'>Ac 10:42</a>; <a href='B:510 18:15'>18:15</a>; <a href='B:510 24:10'>24:10</a>; <a href='B:620 4:8'>2 Ti 4:8</a>; <a href='B:650 12:23'>Hb 12:23</a>; <a href='B:660 4:12'>Js 4:12</a>; <a href='B:660 5:9'>5:9</a>.</b> In <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense <b><a href='B:470 12:27'>Mt 12:27</a>; <a href='B:660 2:4'>Js 2:4</a>; <a href='B:660 4:11'>4:11</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> in specialized sense of a leader such as Samuel in Israel’s early history <b>judge <a href='B:510 13:20'>Ac 13:20</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κριτήριον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κριτικός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}